@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5000
@tenantSlug = demo
@adminPhone = 11999999999
@adminPassword = admin123

### Login admin demo
# @name loginBeta
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Barbearia-Slug: {{tenantSlug}}

{
  "telefone": "{{adminPhone}}",
  "senha": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### Identidade do tenant demo (usa token do login acima)
GET {{baseUrl}}/barbearia/identidade
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBeta.response.body.data.token}}
X-Barbearia-Slug: {{tenantSlug}}
